metadata.name: StCar
metadata.description:
A school break while near Pan Pet - Myanmar. Met a school break while riding on an off the beaten track in the north of Inle Lake. 
How lucky the ones who can see the smile of the children not only in their face also in their eyes.

Location: Pan Pet / Myanmar (2021)

Photographer: Volkan Colak

Edition: 1/1

4000 × 6000px
